/lXmPWiRajsEQtlbjSth3FrlBwtQIwcx7LQdgU3tOamesAjR75DsBTutjA8FL-Wvxncj7qgsC-_7-7Q-cniAu1vOa63mhJMHa0nAo0x_ISmZpg4I6cLRVKc2eQckx7nvj7P-dsdT_1JQQskcABbZjm8Ur2luqNgdPS1xg1iAg146aU4oD8eV90LSuzZ-rJJTAaEU2YUQCGNHHuEfZrJBT1ngMaWkyWDfjn3AvWLTvdZuH8EL9Bg22oXwsCJ9vRK_Xo0Ac_ZkNuBsO7BMGAKvCCjbYrt8hORgGMUfByzVkSyv8SQPQlz9HphKYPRbi9vKBwR6kEiM5ASPczeiGJRsJA8oAuyMFeOs1pH6gJs86naPvEfjFYdPmUifhZLc/yI_0I-OKyJVry9RN-ti42XJ5gg--0bdV/18" target="_blank"&gt;机器狗“Spot”&lt;/a&gt;吗？）并吸引了特斯拉和英伟达的顶尖人才后，它向机器人技术领域投入了数十亿美元。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;经济学正在引起人们的注意。&lt;/strong&gt;如果价格为 10 万美元，Atlas 的运营成本将低于 7.25 美元的联邦最低工资，并且远低于汽车工厂典型的每小时 20 至 38 美元。分析师估计，一旦 2028 年进入“劳动力市场”，它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KZo_jwEdWdpwsZQzNDyAXaNDT7UwsHXDSEtKmoxeAw42ajFcEYQYtxPO94cBDjA33AkhSsjnEL6hk3z5r2lXe6kV8Jx6dUSOn7uPB55YSwcc1jq_N8o5vXBYutnCm2qMvzNRBJE4BZ1WMqqjPKdzGZaJlJoGY6_VxyYJqSSf27b5rPjKFB_MYVMw8BIvjyLAD89FjwR5XV1Xyv4dwse7lRLu-m5jCRbCd3yD5pPsqleyMAcRSpK_3aSqvWMbtyBjH7IMxw_SET_Vl0V2IQp6unA55v1gbiFnTEmQMF7wx3eQIOC19V0UUtb2kDxvJd-nsNiK5DqVicvGMOMjOtHEUqbBcADB4t0Syz7YwRLQ9q4h8DKrH3PSDqOxXSU/4Db5Q34jFpQlM7a1mBYbAgezEDttcg5V/18" target="_blank"&gt;可能会取代&lt;/a&gt;全球 300 万至 400 万装配工人。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;但竞争很激烈。&lt;/strong&gt;据 Omdia 称，去年全球出货的约 13,000 个人形机器人中， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/21V0kjrg4z9XTwJJBKTBt-1GIp69RgbBFzk4CoZ7j1Nd2tLxVNYDQlcKiSzw7eYQxJxQOgY1KnD-59UnaJRB5SXEM5mdRzaQblqYpI6o3ST6rLPlEOIaGFKqKCeiDfzYQ89ZwYe2bvuK-h9tuPA4cEjpanAVmB71A8bPHbxjvVoPa3wVD7Fh-a1-8rMg76-67C6BAqV72tLlL9ytOPmp2Jz42UYtckMO6HvRoWGSI9owuWkhX5FYLByKUMAxyNAGa8UwA85N3iTF3d8KH5QZBRd6LaLX6QfD2DTksTk3NzhgPsNcQp7JsmCWYYiv_zZzg-y8BXoZj5vJ9b2RTdNnCtNQFK16PefitJNiRCdOAR14pqKQ0kooHc8UWVA/bUfz8VkMJVDygyWyOyGbdbo4q2yS6FvT/18" target="_blank"&gt;绝大多数是&lt;/a&gt;中国制造商生产的。它们也更便宜：Unitree Robotics 列出的最新型号售价为 4,900 美元，而 AgiBot 的缩小版售价约为 14,000 美元。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;即便如此，投资者仍押注&lt;/strong&gt;现代汽车能够将其规模、工程实力和先行者雄心转化为优势，这就是其&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/beXi_J5514uVckXmB20utsa7pO7-dxjmmjQXT-6OE2kWZV0vfWY7dYqn9qsJ_OzxZTLn9m5raATZ2cGeK0re0zigcZCPCxlP450B0oykwVRNEbpPfDaIpw4GVSgwUYoeoKHsCqgnDsZ74IARqPmlWYJERmTn-hl3VXOE0Gk8AWIjWgUtl_pvvD1eW_S2GR3xuZAFH6TQBYOyOz6zsNwrw1jvr-d8B5hP02zqF7q-h4xuqty0Csi0emHWVCwxYnnCHClRgayvLzobv21caH8CKqs7f8i97yR3hY96EEeopxBkm9QR8ks6cDFKFfT5ToOaARwNHj787IxmiQUoNF65pOu0jus2WhOE4p2Ll4qzVouuRPxrK8p5VMrfCVI/OzBYFsK87-LmdwHvauPoyzDp5TxwaaaO/18" target="_blank"&gt;股价飙升的&lt;/a&gt;原因。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/VMt6Jm_ovVDmTIGToXOTXhJyQS-uTvXHkBjPc8T13CiwHtjzopkdQlfCtSu6JMSEXoKtlrFaq0-bnofCja33Y7SgOtCwStIrxx460jwyuXHbJ0eZJ9_hPykCR9iYig3wz2rmOcJWMMxsAhCETPUwPNwRjXjlX1DFLJcme8g-IAEhZhgo4QZr1JR95NTgOFFqYngm92rLIaLDnVNlkEIbgRu0ISR3gIiQ0PZF6jO_oRg70KlYKTa8yA-3XaPKCbo0Kd70SaAoa6pSgjaRSTbVZ0_GwPI0bXrOkDXxm1-k4KjFGHuRqEFXn_AYbe1ooz110p-aAw9qBxbk73uce22ROdazg7taYD5Ievarv-fcjpFmm1_m0bLifG6QTHM/YJxsFB8WrHNbo0ekKd1wZWGTHm1EMquc/18" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/if7UZ2REtSdc/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/if7UZ2REtSdc/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKs